#   VNC SSH Tunnel Instructions   #
###################################

* Ensure you have a VNC Client installed on your local machine
* Run the command below to start the SSH tunnel for VNC 

    ssh -L 61000:localhost:5901 -N -l {{ vnc_username }} {{ ansible_fqdn }}

